并以W（双）征服KAWAII（可爱）世界为目标。</p><p>各公司的角色如下。</p><blockquote><p>・Asobi系统：人才发现、真实制作与管理・Activ8：IP开发、虚拟制作、内容策划与制作・Pony Canyon：音乐制作与推广</p></blockquote><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/a81f2f7a10c73042ac1b587b7a31c78e-kix.mh0olakx9kjd-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/a81f2f7a10c73042ac1b587b7a31c78e-kix.mh0olakx9kjd-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/a81f2f7a10c73042ac1b587b7a31c78e-kix.mh0olakx9kjd-jpg.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/a81f2f7a10c73042ac1b587b7a31c78e-kix.mh0olakx9kjd-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/a81f2f7a10c73042ac1b587b7a31c78e-kix.mh0olakx9kjd-768x432.webp 768w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> Activ8 和 Asobi System 成立了角色人才经纪公司“ <a href="https://annin.inc/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ANNIN</a> ”，并负责音乐单元“ <a href="https://x.com/CAPSULEOFFICIAL" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CAPSULE</a> ”的虚拟现场表演“CAPSULE Live in VRChat &#39;Metropulse&#39;”的综合制作。 </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/08/VRChat_2023-08-05_20-23-35.664_2560x1440-3a41b02055e655d6d7e2bb60b5b9e911-kix.5rwk1vr3cqw0-300x169.png"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal"> CAPSULE的VR直播是“FREEDOM”！ “新复古”精神是通过破坏舞台概念而出现的。</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2">如果有人说“这是我第一次看到VR直播”，那人一定会很高兴。 CAPSULE 的首次 VR 直播“CAPSULE Live in VRChat “Metropulse””将于 8 月 5 日星期六在 VRCha 上举行 [...]</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2">VR聊天</span><span class="text-muted small ml-1">2023.08.08</span></div></div></div><p>此外，Activ8还