oads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.1ys7egh584l4-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.1ys7egh584l4-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 942px) 100vw, 942px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.1ys7egh584l4-jpg.webp 942w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.1ys7egh584l4-276x300.webp 276w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.1ys7egh584l4-768x835.webp 768w" width="942" height="1024" /></a></p><p>招聘期：2024年6月21日，星期五 -  7月21日（太阳）</p><p> “ Live”的Upland进行了VTUBER生产。那些通过试镜的人将作为活动基金支付300,000日元。高地由高地承担。除了借用分销所需的设备外，我们还计划支持业务计划。受欢迎的条件包括格斗游戏，Mahjong和每周超过5次。</p><p> <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfL9Zp5ug21jXoZ12ahyz4ve4n8FV2GH0EGHM36IaUt-RHgXg/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>以获取试听申请。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://appland.co.jp/audition/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方网站</a></p><h2 id="link2">VDOL生产</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7